* Wang, Wenfei, Shangyi Zhou, and C. Cindy Fan. &quot;Growth and Decline of Muslim Hui Enclaves in Beijing&quot; (Archive). &quot;Eurasian Geography and Economics&quot;, 2002, 43, No. 2, pp. 104–122. DOI 10.1080/10889388.2002.10641195
